Plugin: french-punctuation
Summary: input helper for more correct spacing in french text
Release: 0.5
TeXmacs: 1.0.2
Author: David Allouche
License: GNU GPL v2.0 or later

TeXmacs has some built-in support for french typographical rules
regarding spacing before punctuation. Generally, line breaking is
disabled before or after some punctuations.

However, the exact rules from the "Imprimerie Nationale" are more elaborate than this. Several punctuation must be preceded by a "rigid thin space", 
